  53,42,"thuma yujza al'iinsan ealaa saeyah aljaza' almstkml lajamie emlh, wann 'iilaa rabik -ayha alrswl- aintiha' jmye khalaqah yawm alqyamt"
  53,43,"wanh subhanah wteala 'adhak man sha' fi aldunya bi'ana srrah, wabka min sha' bi'ana ghammah"
