  54,5,"hdha alquran aldhy ja'ahum hikmat ezymt balighat ghaytha, fa'aya shay' tughni alnudhur ean qawm 'aeraduu wkdhdhabu bha?"
  54,6,"faerd -ayha alrswl- enhm, wantazir bihim ywmana ezymana. yawm yadeu almalik bnfkhh fi \"alqrn\" 'iilaa 'amr fzye mnkr, wahu mawqif alhsab"
  54,7,"dhlylt 'absaruhum yakhrujun min alqubur ka'anahum fi antsharhm wasureat syrhm llhsab jrad muntashir fi alafaq, msreyn 'iilaa ma dueuu 'ilyh, yaqul alkafrwn: hdha yawm easir shadid alhwl"
  54,8,"dhlylt 'absaruhum yakhrujun min alqubur ka'anahum fi antsharhm wasureat syrhm llhsab jrad muntashir fi alafaq, msreyn 'iilaa ma dueuu 'ilyh, yaqul alkafrwn: hdha yawm easir shadid alhwl"